  <text x="140" y="295" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="14" fill="#000">Cat Score = Σ (tag <tspan font-weight="bold">T</tspan> weight) where <tspan font-weight="bold">T</tspan> contains cat</text>
